  <summary date="2005-09-09T15:38:15Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Designates March 8, 2006, as Endangered Species Day.

Encourages: (1) educational entities to spend at least 30 minutes on such Day teaching students about threats to, and the restoration of, endangered species; and (2) organizations, businesses, and agencies with an interest in conserving endangered species to collaborate on educational information for use in schools.</summary>
